## 1. Workflow
• **Doc-first:** No feature code may be merged until its related spec section is approved.
• **LangGraph-first:** Until Phase P5 is done, UI branches may depend only on released LangGraph package.
• **Branching:** `main` → stable; feature branches `feat/<scope>`; docs branches `docs/<topic>`.
• **Commits:** Conventional Commits format.
• **PR requirements:** Green CI, linked milestone (P1…P9), reviewer approval.

